{"id": 1740, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些东西的排序给你带来了困扰？", "description": "最搞不懂的就是，“默认排序”和“智能排序”都是个啥排法？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 11156, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170613235247keua0Y8n2WrmjyHA.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-15T17:00:33Z", "questions": [{"id": 2448, "title": "哪些东西的排序给你带来了困扰？", "content": "哪些东西的排序给你带来了困扰？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 212835, "content": "电商和点评网站的“综合排序”“智能排序”最前面都是广告", "image": "img/option/option/20170614133645iuL8XfE7ISeb1T2J.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212838, "content": "用“销量 or 人气优先”吧，又是可怕的爆款和网红店", "image": "img/option/option/20170614134629AS4u9XGOQ6tqfZ5w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212847, "content": "为了品质按照价格从高到低排吧，最前面又都是9999元的“未上架商品”", "image": "img/option/option/20170614140127CbIa8yiAmwjp4O9F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212858, "content": "微博的时间线是个谜，经常刷到我没关注的和好几天前的内容", "image": "img/option/option/20170614142509becf6x2vBQ1OkqK9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212860, "content": "知乎问题下的回答排序也搞不清楚，经常看完一个答案才发现后面有更精彩的", "image": "img/option/option/20170614142833y1chQzBZSdtfq78i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212864, "content": "微信之类聊天工具的自带表情包能不能允许排序，几个常用表情都不在最前面，心累", "image": "img/option/option/20170614144027E6H5Mjewg03Wxv7a.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212871, "content": "输入法会把我通讯录里的人名或者一些我从没用过的词排前面，却找不到我最常用的词", "image": "img/option/option/201706141447316UJwaAXuPeOZCl5N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 212874, "content": "阅读应用里的热门新闻，虽然有“猜你喜欢”，但最前面都不是我想看的", "image": "img/option/option/20170614145504VJ2y0Wi3aPIN1thg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}